{"tid":1469402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各位今日記得係刺激機場消費,唔係去示威啊","createTime":"2019-08-14T01:43:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T01:48:03.000Z","uid":146699,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1e31ac5a7878eb985365841ede5edd4e504e7bd1","tid":1469402,"uid":146699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"今日係機場行行企企,食飯shopping大行動正式開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今日大家都係消費者,記得著便服去機場睇下戲食個飯放鬆心情,食飽又可以行下<br />\n今日係唔需要示威叫口號,有文宣可以放係當眼處任人取閱<br />\n<br />\n得閑記得排下departure條隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過記得唔好阻人上機啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家玩得開心又放心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"597f5c7c7477be0e3cb5aa90a4a2f3ef9fe01c37","tid":1469402,"uid":95487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:43:20.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">求求大家唔好再執著於捉鬼</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n鬼一定有，唔會捉得晒<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">今次捉到既鬼唔會係第一隻<br />\n更加唔會係最後一隻</span><br />\n<br />\n我地有<span style=\"color: gold;\">連儂牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">撕一貼百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中共有<span style=\"color: gold;\">防火牆</span>，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">捉一滲百</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">捉鬼唔係重點呀大家<br />\n提醒同路人提防就夠</span></span><br />\n<br />\n利申 其實打鬼/狗並唔反感<br />\n但我唔希望大家係咁既氛圍下打<br />\n好易失去理智，anyway 核爆都唔割<br />\n慶幸我身邊既和理優都話星期六會再入機場<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">818見！五大訴求，缺一不可！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<del><span style=\"color: violet;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">題外話，下次唔好咁突然除褲好唔好</span></span></del><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2693c608265d931f4afb1f721b20cf290632a5d","tid":1469402,"uid":146699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:44:04.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"15c0df0c18edc5c0ed7b484bb58fa023ad18a9c7","tid":1469402,"uid":146699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:44:16.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ad2f05e855fb4b38872ec0ad81e319cb4924d490","tid":1469402,"uid":146699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T01:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a13c6ce8a87011fe6b3f4dec33fa7f3090380a4f","tid":1469402,"u